 the long-term contract will be replaced by short-term visits that would take place over a period of one (1) more year. These visits will be needed particularly during the crucial periods of budget preparation. The PIBA will work closely with the Senior Public Finance Adviser responsible for overall budget management and, in the conduct of training programs, will receive support from the Budget Technicians (para. 2.13). The PIBA will coordinate the work of the four PIP Specialists (mentioned in para. 2.41) and will also be assisted by them. - training programs prepared by the PIBA; and - office equipment to be identified by the PIBA.
